custom properties set & @apply
Allows you to store a set of properties in a named custom property, then
reference them in other style rules.
:root {
  --danger-theme: {
    color: white;
    background-color: red;
  }
}

.danger {
  @apply --danger-theme;
}

⚠️
The definitions are limited to :root selector.
